title: The Housemaid
overview: The Housemaid tells us about a girl, Zhang Pan, who comes to Beijing from a small city with a big city dream. But she has to start with the lowly job as a housemaid. At a wealthy client's home, she is lured to wear sexy suits to work for more tips. She want to resist but her financial difficulties gave her no choice. Her younger brother came to her and saw his sister's living skills in Beijing.
